cken stock paste (see Tips)","50 g tomato paste","1 tsp salt, plus extra for seasoning","1 tsp freshly ground black pepper, plus extra for seasoning","6 lamb shanks","100 g plain flour","200 g carrot, cut into pieces (1-2 cm)","200 g zucchini, cut into pieces (1-2 cm)","100 g pitted green Sicilian olives","220 g dried risoni pasta"]},{"title":"Feta Topping","content":["2 garlic cloves","4 sprigs fresh flat-leaf parsley, leaves only","4 sprigs fresh thyme, leaves only","¼ tsp dried chilli flakes","30 g olive oil","20 g lemon juice","200 g firm feta cheese, cut into cubes (2 cm)"]}],"id":"r103488","imageLink":"https:\/\/3.bp.blogspot.com\/-SOYh5OR_PHk\/XZQxBeOKK7I\/AAAAAAAAcq0\/TlrM7h7ThDoqmrW0aWTjMQrxN7lQTvReACLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_k5QFpReqfiVV8lhe.png","title":"Lamb shanks with risoni and feta","publishedAt":"2016-06-19T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"41.8 g","fat":"32.6 g","uom":"per 1 portions","carbohydrates":"46.3 g","calories":"2775 kJ \/ 660 kcal"},"usefulItems":"snaplock bag, large frying pan, casserole dish (28 cm), aluminium foil, bowl, 6 serving bowls, oven, stove top","basicInfo":["easy","30m","3h 50m","6 portions"]}